channel.title: Surface tension Crashs
channel.description:
Passing through the tunnel after the tank fight I am getting the crash CUtlLinkedList overflow! (exhausted index range). Whenever I try to open the door regardless of settings.
My map location is Bm_c2a5g. I cant pass through the door without the game crashing.
